<H3> <TI>   Government Drafts Decree on Agro-Industrial Reorganization </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PM1301113794 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 13 Jan 94 
First Edition p 3 </F>

<F P=103> PM1301113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Latest Reorganization"] </F>
  [Text] We learned from informed sources that the 
government has prepared a draft decree "On the Functioning of 
the Russian Federation Agro-Industrial Complex in 1994," whereby 
the Ministry of Agriculture and Food is to become the central 
federal executive organ in charge of agriculture and the 
agro-industrial complex. 
  The reorganized ministry is assigned the functions of 
forming 
state food and raw material resources of grain and oil-seed crop 
seeds, and new departments for the food and processing industry, 
the mixed feed industry, and for procurement and produce 
shipment are to be set up within the ministry. 
  What is more, there are plans to set up a number of sector 
state, state/cooperative, and state/joint-stock formations under 
the ministry with shared participation, delegating to these 
formations certain state management functions with regard to 
fundamental specialized sectors. 

</TEXT>

