<F P=101> Kazakhstan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Details of Nurmagambetov's Visit </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PM1201132794 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 12 Jan 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> PM1201132794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Anatoliy Ladin report under the "Yesterday" rubric: </F>
"Defense Ministers Will Meet"] 
  [Text] At the invitation of Army General Chi Haotian, PRC 
defense minister, Army General Sagadat Nurmagambetov, defense 
minister of the Republic of Kazakhstan, will visit China 11-14 
January. While in Beijing, the head of Kazakhstan's military 
department will also meet with Zhang Zhen, deputy chairman of 
the PRC Central Military Commission. 
  The talks will cover an exchange of experience in the 
education and instruction of personnel, the training of cadres, 
and other problems of military cooperation between the two 
states, the press service of the defense minister of Kazakhstan 
has reported. 

</TEXT>

