<F P=100> Federal Assembly </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shumeyko Elected </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1301111594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1100 GMT 
13 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1301111594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vladimir Shumeyko was today elected chairman of the 
Federation Council in the Federal Assembly of the Russian 
Federation. He got 98 votes in a secret ballot. His main 
rival, Petr Romanov, got 52 votes. Eduard Rossel got six votes, 
and Kirsan Ilumzhinov seven votes. 

</TEXT>

