<H3> <TI>   Duma `Groups' Reach Agreement on Procedural Issues </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1201175294 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1600 GMT 
12 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1201175294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


