Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At today's sitting, the leaders of the Duma groups 
[fraktsii] reached agreement over a number of procedural 
matters. Members of the Council of Elders, made up of 
representatives from each of the groups, will chair tomorrow's 
sitting, an RIA correspondent has learned. 
  The sitting's agenda includes the question of endorsing the 
temporary rules of procedure governing the work of the chamber, 
as well as the election of the Duma chairman and his deputies. 

