<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Corrections"] </F>
  [Text] According to the Russian Federation Central 
Electoral Commission, the published list of deputies of the 
State Duma of the Russian Federation Federal Assembly elected to 
federal electoral districts from the "Liberal-Democratic Party 
of Russia [LDPR]" Electoral Association (ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA 28 
