  Viktor Grigoryevich Vishnyakov, born 1931, Russian, higher 
education, member of the LDPR, thereafter as published; 
  Aleksey Alekseyevich Zuyev, born 1971, Russian, secondary 
technical education, nonparty member, temporarily out of work, 
thereafter as published; 
