<H3> <TI>   Tajik Mojahedin Kill 7 Soldiers in Shurabadskiy </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1301155394 (Clandestine) Voice of Free Tajikistan in Tajik 
0900 GMT 13 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1301155394 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Free Tajikistan </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Tajik </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The news sources of the Islamic Rebirth Party 
reported that Tajik Mojahedin have been carrying out combat 
operations inside Kulyab Oblast and other regions of the 
republic for a long time. 
  In some areas they have infiltrated from three to five 
kilometres deep into the republic. The Tajik Mojahedin carried 
out a successful operation in the village of Sarygor, 
Shurabadskiy rayon, Kulyab Oblast, yesterday, reports the 
source. Government forces that have been supported by Russian 
troops have suffered big losses in the course of this operation. 
  Seven servicemen of the Communist regime have been killed by 
the Tajik Mojahedin as a result of this attack. 

