<H3> <TI>   Clinton Invites Maritime Region Governor to Reception </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1301142594 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1131 GMT 13 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1301142594 </F>
