<F P=102>  LD1301135594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0756 
GMT 13 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1301135594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, 13 Jan (CRIME-PRESS) -- The Russian Internal 
Affairs Ministry's Public Relations Center reports that a 
meeting was held between Russia's Internal Affairs Minister 
Viktor Yerin and Moshe Shahal, Israel's minister of police and 
minister of energy and infrastructure, who is in Moscow on an 
official visit. 
  During the conversation the problems of combating crime and 
the possibility of cooperation between the two countries in this 
sphere were touched upon. The signing of a protocol on the 
